Implemented the tank controller in:

- `components/controller/controller.c`

Behavior now matches the task contract:

- boots safe with pump off
- turns on below `30`
- turns off above `80`
- holds prior output in `30..80`
- ignores short idle gaps
- fails safe on malformed input
- times out to off after `>1000 ms`
- handles explicit sensor-timeout input as safe off

